  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK430">
<l>aṟivuṭaiyā rellā muṭaiya raṟivilā</l>
<l>reṉṉuṭaiya rēṉu milar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who possess wisdom, possess every thing; those who have not wisdom, whatever they may possess, have nothing.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
